content:
Yeah, I was really glad I packed those. The rain boots were especially helpful since I didn't have to worry about getting my feet wet. And the extra jacket kept me warm and dry. I think one of the highlights of the trip was when we all went out for dinner on Sunday and had a great time catching up. It was nice to just relax and be with family.

Now that I'm back, I need to get organized again. I was thinking of doing a major clean-out of my bag to get rid of any unnecessary items and make sure everything is still organized. Do you have any tips on how to do that effectively?
